<h3 style="margin-top:-10px;">Welcome to PEARL</h3>

<br />

<div class="alert-info" style="padding:25px; margin-bottom:25px;">

    <p style="font-size:1.5em;">
        "The aim of	the	PEARL project is to	improve	outcomes for patients and families by using	patient	experience	to	enhance	the	behavioural	skills	of	clinical staff in acute	care".	
    </p>

    <hr />

    <p style="font-size:1.2em;">
        Using quantitative & qualitative study linking experiential and performance measures with iterative feedback through ethnography and behaviour change theory, PEARL will produce a <em>reflective learning framework</em> with content adaptable to local context.
    </p>

</div>

